roborick007@... writes:

> Kup: Grimlock?! Is that you, lad? How can any of you Dinobots be here? I 
> thought the last of the Autobot ranks were killed when the Tripredacus took 
> over Cbertron.
> 
> 

Grimlock looked over at the old bot. "Kup... he laughed transforming and 
looked at Kup remembering their last time meeting durring the unicron war... "Tell 
GrimLock good part." He relaxed knowing no harm was coming...

Scourge's evil laughter burst through the air. "I am not the commander of the 
ark?" Maxima my dear, you should scurry back to hydras, other then that your 
all on dangerous ground, the grounds around here now belong to the teracons, 
leave now or prepare for battle."
